<p>An <b>endangered language</b> is a <a href="/wiki/Language" title="Language">language</a> that is at risk of falling out of use, generally because it has few surviving speakers. If it loses all of its native speakers, it becomes an <i><a href="/wiki/Extinct_language" title="Extinct language">extinct language</a></i>.</p>
<table id="toc" class="toc" summary="Contents">
